text: Roquetaillade-et-Conilhac is a commune of 277 people (2017). It is in the region Occitanie in the Aude department in the south of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2019 and consists of the former communes of Roquetaillade (the seat) and Conilhac-de-la-Montagne.Arrêté préfectoral 5 December 2018 == References == Category:2019 establishments in France Category:Communes in Aude
title: Roquetaillade-et-Conilhac
